nodes.text: Rrabel Dage was a Duros Loyalist from the planet Duro. During the Yuuzhan Vong War and just prior to the Battle of Duro, he protested allowing refugees to relocate to Duro and planned to use his contacts with the Bburru Docking Authority to sabotage emergency supplies being transported by CorDuro Shipping to the refugee settlements. Unbeknownst to Dage, the supplies were secretly being diverted to Urrdorf City by Durgard Brarun, a Yuuzhan Vong collaborator on the CorDuro Executive Committee.
